_sText:
The 2 bomb sites are located in the middle of the map, one on the second story, and the other on top story.  The glass is breakable but is hard to break.  There is also a basement, 2 sniper pits (but watch out there is a grate floor above you) and 2 other larger towers. 

Fun to Play when-
Gravity is set to 200 and knives only
